content: The best ever app ... at 3am on call even better !!!
I want to be able to change the order of the categories to what I need it for the most. It's missing dextrose dosing.
Great idea and very good layout (though an age vs wt option would be great). Only flaw is lack of customising regarding drugs (ie adding drugs).

As useful as it may be, this app is not very good. You can't customize it to your own technique, it has no IM dosing and doesn't have actual drug referencing/pharmacology for other drugs we use in this population. Buy a better app this one's not worth it in my opinion
In the field a good quick reference guide is crucial when the time keeps ticking. Easy to navigate and accurate information. A must in my opinion if you prefer digital over flipbook.
All this info is on the code sheets at yr pts bedside.  Waste of money
Safe dose app includes how many cc's to draw up based on standard concentrations. Otherwise this is a great app.
SUPER one of the best medical programs out.
Just downloaded and first thing I noticed is that ET tube sizes are incorrect. Will look over but if something that basic is wrong, I wasted money.
Great app it is like a digital broslow with more information. Very useful for doseing for rsi and in codes.
Starting a peds rotation next month and this is going to be a life saver. Everything you need for each particular weight. A little pricey but sweet!
